                <p style="/*! color: red; */font-size: 0.75em;">Note. Free accounts are limited to processing @siteConfig.Value.GlobalRateLimit analyses at a time, up to @siteConfig.Value.GlobalAnalysisCap per day.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-default btn-lg" asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Dashboard">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-3 col-md-push-3">
        <div class="panel panel-primary pricing-panel" style="border-color: lightgrey;">
            <div class="panel-heading" style="background-color: #03326883;border-color:lightgray;color:black;height:6em;">
                <h3 class="panel-title"></h3><h3>Subscriber<p style="font-size: 0.75em;margin-top: 0.25em;">Personal or Organisation</p></h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>Analyse a seascape up to ten decimal degrees squared. Each analysis includes:</p>   
                <ul>
                    <li style="line-height: 2em;">One Marine LEFT Report</li><li style="line-height: 2em;">Download of Underlying Data</li>
                    <li style="line-height: 2em;">API for custom data packages</li><li style="line-height: 1.35em;">Greater concurrency to suit your organisation</li>
                </ul>
                <a class="btn btn-default btn-lg" asp-action="Contact" asp-controller="Home">Inquire</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

